episodes.title: Tony Morris and the Hypocricy of Watchtower's Leadership
episodes.description: Caught in the Largest Discount Liquor Store in northern New Jersey, Tony Morris caught at 11:00 a.m. on a Sunday morning with a cart full of expensive whiskey causes an uproar among the Ex-JW community causing yet another incident that induces close scrutiny of the hypocrisy of the body of cruel men who set themselves as the moral voice  of Jehovah’s Witnesses.
